Lost In A Desert Storm | The Mourning | Survival Thriller Movie

Twenty years after going MIA in Desert Storm, Aaron returns home under mysterious conditions, not having aged since his disappearance, and must re-establish relationships with loved ones before an imminent return to an ambiguous other-worldly existence.

2015.  Stars: Michael Rene Walton, Louis Mandylor, Dominique Swain
